IMAPStore fastmail-remote
Host imap.fastmail.com
User james@jamesbvaughan.com
PassCmd "pass fastmail.com/mutt"
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt
SSLType IMAPS

MaildirStore fastmail-local
Path ~/.mail/
Inbox ~/.mail/Inbox

Channel fastmail
Master :fastmail-remote:
Slave :fastmail-local:
Patterns "INBOX" "Archive" "Sent" "Drafts" "Apartment Hunting" "Work"
Create Both
